front.title: •Amanaman
front.gametext: Once per battle, may use 2 Force to 'behead' (place out of play) one opposing non-droid character lost or forfeited where present. Adds X to attrition in battles at same site where X = the number of 'beheaded' victims.
front.lore: Male Amanin. Hangs the heads of his victims on his staff. Nicknamed Amanaman; his real name is unknown on Tatooine.
